{"product_id":"nurme-ylang-ylang-shampoo-pro-vit-b5-250ml","title":"NURME Ylang-Ylang Shampoo ProVitamin B5 250ml","description":"\u003cp\u003eNurme organic shampoo is based on raw materials recognized by eco-certifications. The shampoo contains only plant-based ingredients. It is gentle for your hair and for the environment.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eYlang-Ylang shampoo helps to reduce hair loss and balance dry scalp. Ylang-ylang essential oil is known as a good moisturizer and it also promotes hair regrowth. Ylang-ylang has a sweet floral scent and reminds you those warm summer days.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe shampoo contains gentle surfactants that create a creamy lather and are mild on the skin. The hair-strengthening ProVitamin B5 helps reduce hair damage and split ends.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/strong\u003eUse the shampoo together with ylang-ylang hair conditioner to make your hair silky, easy to comb, and shiny from roots to ends.\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e Aqua, Coco-Glucoside, Sodium Coco-Sulfate, Sodium Chloride, Panthenol (Provitamin B5), Citric Acid, Hydrolyzed Wheat Protein, Glyceryl Oleate, Sodium Benzoate, Potassium Sorbate, Cananga Odorata (Ylang Ylang) Flower Oil, Linalool*.\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e*Occurs naturally in essential oil\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e0% Parabens | 0% Silicones | 0% Synthetic and fragrances\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c!----\u003e","brand":"Nurme","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":49553854824775,"sku":null,"price":10.5,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/nurme-ylang-ylang-shampoo-provitamin-b5-250ml-446160.jpg?v=1739897237","url":"